question What does the name Scroll refer to?

paragraph
 <em>A scroll</em> is a single folder containing Scrolldown files and a `scroll.settings` file.
 Scroll compiles those Scrolldown files into a static
 index.html page.

paragraph
 Scroll is also the name of the command line app that includes a
 simple fs watch app for live preview.

paragraph
 Scrolldown is the name of a Tree Language defined in this grammarğŸ”—github.com/publicdomaincompany/scroll/blob/main/scrolldown.grammar.

